data.description: Located in the Fox Creek Subdivision, this spacious home offers 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths and 2184 square feet of living space. Located on the first level, you will find ample space to entertain in the family room featuring a wood burning fireplace. The kitchen is open to the family room on one side and the formal dining on the other. Just off of the family room is a conveniently located half bathroom, perfect for guest use. Once you head upstairs you will find the secondary bedrooms are located on the right side of home and share a full size bathroom. The primary bedroom is on the left, secluded from the secondary rooms allowing for privacy. The primary bathroom offers dual vanities and a large walk-in closet. This home is equipped with a water-softener system that will convey with the property. You must see this home to appreciate all it has to offer!
